statements: SELECT * FROM real_estate_properties WHERE state='CA';
SELECT property_name, address, city FROM real_estate_properties WHERE zip_code='90210';
SELECT property_id, purchase_price, estimated_rent FROM real_estate_properties WHERE state='NY' ORDER BY purchase_price DESC;

SELECT property_name, state, estimated_rent FROM real_estate_properties WHERE city='Miami' ORDER BY property_name;
SELECT * FROM real_estate_properties WHERE state = 'CA';
SELECT property_name, city, current_value FROM real_estate_properties WHERE purchase_price > 500000 ORDER BY current_value DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_name, address, city, state, zip_code FROM real_estate_properties WHERE state = 'NY' AND estimated_rent >= 2000 ORDER BY property_id ASC;

SELECT * FROM real_estate_properties WHERE purchase_price BETWEEN 300000 AND 400000 ORDER BY purchase_price ASC;
SELECT * FROM property;
SELECT property_name, address, current_value FROM property WHERE property_type='House';
SELECT property_name, purchase_price FROM property ORDER BY purchase_price DESC;
SELECT AVG(current_value) AS avg_value FROM property;
SELECT property_name, profit FROM property p INNER JOIN financial_report fr ON p.property_id = fr.property_id WHERE fr.report_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM property;
SELECT property_name, address FROM property WHERE property_type = 'House';
SELECT property_id, property_name, purchase_price FROM property ORDER BY purchase_price DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_name, revenue, profit FROM property JOIN financial_report ON property.property_id = financial_report.property_id;
SELECT property_name, revenue, profit FROM property JOIN financial_report ON property.property_id = financial_report.property_id WHERE profit > 10000;
SELECT * FROM investment_properties;
SELECT property_name, property_type, market_value FROM investment_properties ORDER BY market_value DESC;

SELECT * FROM investment_properties ORDER BY purchase_price DESC, property_name ASC;
SELECT property_name, property_type, market_value FROM investment_properties WHERE property_type='Residential' AND market_value > 100000;
SELECT property_id, property_name, purchase_price FROM investment_properties WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01';

SELECT property_type, target_market, expected_roi, risk_level FROM investment_opportunities WHERE expected_roi > 10 AND risk_level='Low' ORDER BY expected_roi DESC;
SELECT * FROM properties ORDER BY property_name ASC;
SELECT id, property_name, address, type FROM properties WHERE type = 'Residential';

SELECT p.property_name, r.report_name FROM properties p INNER JOIN reports r ON p.id = r.property_id;

SELECT * FROM properties WHERE type = 'Apartment' ORDER BY purchase_price DESC
SELECT property_name, address, market_value FROM properties WHERE market_value > 100000 ORDER BY property_name ASC

SELECT p.property_name, t.transaction_date, t.amount FROM properties p JOIN transactions t ON p.id = t.property_id WHERE t.amount > p.market_value ORDER BY t.amount DESC
